com.ezrebclan.asset.Saveable

    • Uses of Saveable in com.ezrebclan.asset

      Classes in com.ezrebclan.asset that implement Saveable 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Asset<Type>
      An Asset is anything that gets loaded by your code.
      class  BigTextAsset
      A Big Text Asset is multiple lines of text, stored in a string array.
      If you need to store a single line of text, look into a Small Text Asset.
      class  ImageAsset
      An ImageAsset holds a BufferedImage as its data.
      ImageAssets also includes extra data in its AssetIndex: X Resolution (Width) Y Resolution (Hieght) Full Resolution (WidthxHieght)
      class  SmallTextAsset
      A Small Text Asset is a single line of text.
      If you need to store multiple lines of text, look into a Big Text Asset.
